[[File:Ned_Stark.jpg|thumb|264px|Will is executed for breaking his oath]]'''Desertion''' is a serious crime in the [[Seven Kingdoms]]. It takes place when a man abandons his post, particularly in times of war. Deserters are considered [[outlaw]]s and thus are marked for death.

Within the ranks of the [[Night's Watch]], desertion is considered a form of [[oathbreaking]]. Deserters are not only hunted down by sworn brothers of the Watch but also by lords should a deserter enter his lands.
